title: President Donald J. Trump Has Secured a Tremendous Victory For American Farmers and Businesses With New Japan Trade Agreements – The White House
content:
Fact Sheets			

		Economy & Jobs	

Issued on:
October 7, 2019
This is a huge victory for America’s farmers, ranchers, and growers. And that’s very important to me.
						President Donald J. Trump					IMPROVING TRADE WITH JAPAN: The United States and Japan are signing two new agreements to improve our strong trade relationship.EXPANDING MARKETS FOR AMERICAN FARMERS: President Trump continues to secure fairer markets for American farmers.PROMOTING DIGITAL TRADE: President Trump is working to expand the vital digital trade between the United States and Japan.
